{"tid":542622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金融時報：文翠珊拒支持一帶一路　訪華行程蒙陰影","createTime":"2018-01-27T16:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T02:02:54.000Z","uid":48083,"like":168,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"91feef8918a0de3b871f88de861a40cf4520d6fc","tid":542622,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"英國首相文翠珊下周三（31日）展開一連3天訪華行程前夕，英國《金融時報》引述消息稱，她因為拒絕正式支持中國「一帶一路」計劃，令行程蒙上陰影。<br />\n<br />\n文翠珊原定將會在訪華期間，與中國及英國商家召開圓桌會議，商討「一帶一路」投資，但英國官員稱，因為她拒絕正式支持「一帶一路」，會議可能取消。官員指，有關分歧更可能威脅中國國家主席習近平，2015年訪英時締結的雙邊貿易協議，「主要分歧在於中國堅持英國正式支持『一帶一路』」。分歧亦令文翠珊訪華行程安排受阻，中國官員不時拒絕回電話。首相府拒絕評論報道。<br />\n<br />\n中國的「一帶一路」，去年已獲俄羅斯、意大利、希臘及匈牙利等約30國正式支持。但上月將中國定性為「戰略競爭者」的美國，對「一帶一路」抱懷疑，法國總統馬克龍本月亦稱有關計劃的利益應大家同享。英國倫敦政治經濟學院（LSE）中國前瞻計劃（China Foresight）負責人余杰（譯音）稱，中國希望英國正式支持，因為如此的話，其他國家便沒理由拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n英國前首相卡梅倫和時任財相歐思邦，均視中國為改善英國經濟的妙藥，在任期間致力改善雙邊關係，但自文翠珊上台後，中英關係出現倒退。<br />\n<br />\n（金融時報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180127/s00005/1517063610532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180127%2Fs00005%2F1517063610532&d=TCECO9EFxHjleQyVYmg%2BMYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=c3f6d1ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180127%2Fs00005%2F1517063610532&h=bffb45f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180127/s00005/1517063610532</a>"},{"pid":"0a1c4ceec41f633730470e0f8a10ab7664ec47d8","tid":542622,"uid":35870,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce8d1f4ecabf85bfac93c8c76cf0a695b2b3dda","tid":542622,"uid":79563,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「主要分歧在於中國堅持英國正式支持『一帶一路』」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCLS, 迫人支持個垃圾計劃？"},{"pid":"e97f1549f2652257bc73d0f69fd1dd3fe0ee68e4","tid":542622,"uid":63669,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"唔知邊個話英國要同中國做生意所以買中國怕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c3c0ebd506ae9fd524878fd5f84451f1b7d4ee","tid":542622,"uid":79563,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:07:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分歧亦令文翠珊訪華行程安排受阻，中國官員不時拒絕回電話。首相府拒絕評論報道。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無撚訪支囉<br />\n<br />\nchina trade根本唔係想像中咁重要"},{"pid":"0f5c8195bde17c475168c743fb4e64cac8eacc97","tid":542622,"uid":119895,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:07:42.000Z","msg":"May姐好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb070f60a9bf3db408865e89df8c39a3161cd89b","tid":542622,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:08:49.000Z","msg":"妙藥定致癌毒藥呀"},{"pid":"fb45594580581daabfc3a8e8099ee771caed6953","tid":542622,"uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e97f1549f2652257bc73d0f69fd1dd3fe0ee68e4","tid":542622,"uid":63669,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"唔知邊個話英國要同中國做生意所以買中國怕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"由有人講尖實力開始，<br />\n支共喺外交俾全世界圍剿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英國婆分分鐘同侵侵有默契玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fdcd86ac50653c935057c64ab5082bb3748dc0","tid":542622,"uid":24730,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:09:31.000Z","msg":"刁老大條撚咁大，幫英國人DQ埋佢啦"},{"pid":"944b7df3570d07b835cf9c4e167320ecb4f4eca3","tid":542622,"uid":36820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持may姐"},{"pid":"d1f36319b50eef680ab5c522b54f8d2eabc4e025","tid":542622,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:17:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19042c1c44c89b3d2445b1802dbb9dd550cfa1f","tid":542622,"uid":47674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:20:59.000Z","msg":"雜種春秋大夢 從來都係自說自話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「一帶一路」係咁 「新型大國關係」又係咁<br />\n只有下面班奴才喺度逢迎"},{"pid":"72eecc1016ee852d053023b84a67adb5c0238cf0","tid":542622,"uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:21:05.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯金融時報》報道，一帶一路涉及34個亞歐國家的交通基礎設施項目，單根據華府國際戰略研究中心的研究，在承接項目的承包商當中，有89%是中國公司，只有11%是其他國家的公司。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，這個差異跟中共宣傳一帶一路的言論不符。中共領導人宣稱讓所有參與者共享利益。<br />\n<br />\n國際戰略研究中心的研究顯示，中共的言行存在巨大的不一致。國際戰略研究中心重接亞洲項目主任希爾曼（Jonathan Hillman）說：「儘管一帶一路的官方言論是開放的，但是它仍然是以中國為中心的努力。」<br />\n<br />\n跟一帶一路形成對比的是，兩大西方多邊開發銀行&mdash;&mdash;世界銀行和亞洲開發銀行的項目承包商的來源分佈更加均勻。<br />\n<br />\n根據國際戰略研究中心的研究，在上述兩大開發銀行資助的交通基礎設施項目中，41%的承包商來自於項目所在國家，29%來自於中國，30%來自於第三方國家。該研究涵蓋了2006年到今天的178個項目。<br />\n<br />\n英國皇家聯合服務學院院長Raffaello Pantucci說，外界現在才明白，中共的一帶一路不是要向外國送錢和輸送合同。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2018-01-26/71187503\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2018-01-26%2F71187503&d=TCECO9EFxHjleQyVYmg%2BMYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a2395d15\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2018-01-26/71187503</a>"},{"pid":"ff6be92c7a59389cd1e1a67cbeffd1a80de1cb01","tid":542622,"uid":147314,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"唔送錢，支那仲有乜野用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911f50be4c327cdc453369fe237b65c1aff3b60b","tid":542622,"uid":4783,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"說好的英國要含中國撚呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e0fb8ea28469c70100b08d8e192c5b72c7915b","tid":542622,"uid":67432,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"May姐都唔撈得耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0112e1deb31b8b1b9c1a5aafde1c9738ae9bb3f5","tid":542622,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fb45594580581daabfc3a8e8099ee771caed6953","tid":542622,"uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e97f1549f2652257bc73d0f69fd1dd3fe0ee68e4","tid":542622,"uid":63669,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"唔知邊個話英國要同中國做生意所以買中國怕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"由有人講尖實力開始，<br />\n支共喺外交俾全世界圍剿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英國婆分分鐘同侵侵有默契玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"reply